explanation: "A 48-year-old with:<br><br>* Progressive dyspnea\n* Dry cough\n* HRCT: **honeycombing + reticular opacities**<br><br>\u00a0**Idiopathic pulmonary fibrosis (a prototype ILD**\n<img src=\"https://corebtr-assets-production.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/question_explanation/b860420b-dd2d-49c9-8fd6-b7a53d716992.jpg\" alt=\"Uploaded Image\">*HRCT of the lungs showing the classical UIP pattern: honeycomb transformation*<br><br>**Classic Imaging:**<br><br>* **Subpleural + basal predominance**\n* **Honeycombing** (clustered cystic air spaces)\n* **Reticular pattern**\n* Traction bronchiectasis\n<br><br><br>| **Type of Crackles** | **Disease** |\n| ---------------- | ------- |\n| **Fine (\u201cVelcro\u201d)** | ILD, pulmonary fibrosis |\n| **Coarse** | Bronchiectasis, pneumonia |\n| Late inspiratory | Fibrosis |\n| Early inspiratory | COPD |",
